  "reference_number": "RUS2419",
  "remarks": "\nNikolay Alexandrovich KAZAKOV is an “involved person” under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following ground: KAZAKOV is or has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by owning or controlling an entity, Donskyie Ugoli Trading House, which is carrying on business in a sector of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian extractives sector. \n",
